{"tid":326922,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"為咗搬出黎住而轉行是否值得","createTime":"2017-07-18T11:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T11:45:39.000Z","uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"053af3aab0467099fe08c8872ef22adede87cb82","tid":326922,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:17:42.000Z","msg":"本身同屋企人住得好地地<br />\n然後因為同其中一個人由細到大都有爭執<br />\n已經頂佢唔順 唔想再對住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同啲唔岩既人住埋一齊真係慘過食十舊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身番office <br />\n如果我轉做sales搵多啲 出黎租樓住<br />\n大家覺得值唔值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：值得，搬出黎唔洗再對住條人渣，乜都抵番哂<br />\n<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：為咗個人而冇哂前途，又做唔到岩自己既工，吞咗佢算啦"},{"pid":"59e6ecbd13f15ba94c36fdccf78ce1ba74d2ca9c","tid":326922,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008d5348dcbb4f545512f048ffe52de7fdcb6f1d","tid":326922,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:45:39.000Z","msg":"開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}